WEBVTT

00:08:27.542 --> 00:08:31.351
that Cocospy allows you
to spy on your wife with ease,

00:08:31.375 --> 00:08:33.601
"You do not have to worry
about where she goes,

00:08:33.625 --> 00:08:36.559
who she talks to
or what websites she visits."

00:08:36.583 --> 00:08:37.833
So that's creepy.

00:08:38.583 --> 00:08:42.143
HelloSpy, which is another such product,

00:08:42.167 --> 00:08:46.809
had a marketing page
in which they spent most of their copy

00:08:46.833 --> 00:08:48.809
talking about the prevalence of cheating

00:08:48.833 --> 00:08:51.518
and how important it is
to catch your partner cheating,

00:08:51.542 --> 00:08:54.559
including this fine picture of a man

00:08:54.583 --> 00:08:57.059
who has clearly just caught
his partner cheating

00:08:57.083 --> 00:08:58.351
and has beaten her.

00:08:58.375 --> 00:09:00.893
She has a black eye,
there is blood on her face.